  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      In the 21st century, threats to human health of new respiratory infectious diseases
      increased.

      The project aim is to establish pneumonia pathogens network in Beijing and understand the
      pathogen spectrum distribution.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
